r the boundaries of legend and the privileges of youth and beauty.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aAmerican poetryzCanaday21st century. 0aDogsvPoetry. 0aGanymede (Greek mythology)vPoetry. 0aGay culturevPoetry. 7aPOETRY / American / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311127268908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2019z978311127498040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978022800058740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780228000587423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780228000587/original  a978-3-11-127268-9  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-127498-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles